query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(k mk mi_idx) NoMergeJoin(k mi_idx mk t) NoMergeJoin(k mi mi_idx mk t it1) NoMergeJoin(it1 k mi mi_idx mk t it2) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS north_european_dark_production
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IS NOT NULL AND k.keyword IN ('superhero',
'fight',
'claw',
'.hack')
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '6.6'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('English',
'America',
'Germany',
'Bulgaria',
'Swedish',
'Denmark',
'Danish',
'Norway',
'Denish',
'Japan')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating'
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('tv mini series',
'episode');
